Interface IObjectBooleanChecker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICheck, IObjectBooleanDefaultCheck, IObjectBooleanDefaultProperties, IObjectBooleanEqualsCheck, IObjectBooleanFalseCheck, IObjectBooleanNotDefaultCheck, IObjectBooleanNotEqualsCheck, IObjectBooleanNotNullCheck, IObjectBooleanNotSameCheck, IObjectBooleanNullCheck, IObjectBooleanSameCheck, IObjectBooleanTrueCheck
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AChecker, Checker

    public interface IObjectBooleanChecker
extends IObjectBooleanSameCheck, IObjectBooleanNotSameCheck, IObjectBooleanEqualsCheck, IObjectBooleanNotEqualsCheck, IObjectBooleanNullCheck, IObjectBooleanNotNullCheck, IObjectBooleanFalseCheck, IObjectBooleanTrueCheck, IObjectBooleanDefaultCheck, IObjectBooleanNotDefaultCheck
    Specification grouping all Boolean check specifications.

    This (or a derivative) should inherit all check methods targeting Boolean.
